data.description: UPDATE: SELLER WILLING TO PAY FOR A  BUY DOWN OF UP TO 2 POINTS OFF THE MARKET RATES WITH ACCEPTED CONTRACT (at sellers discretion based on sell price.) Welcome home to 8303 Smithton Rd a 3 bed, 1.5 bath home in the quiet, established neighborhood of Bittersweet.  As you enter the home you will see a large room at the front of the house, complete with natural wood burning fire place. Hard wood flooring thru out first floor. The kitchen, which is loaded with upgraded stainless steel appliances, including a gas range and plenty of cabinet and counter space, ready for your holiday cooking. Full bath and 3 bedrooms finishes up the first floor.  The master bedroom has a half bath for your conveniences. Heading down into the basement you will find 2 bonus rooms for a larger family or extra guest that need a place to stay.  Open area for gatherings and a laundry room behind closed door. The backyard is fully fenced and has a large deck, offering the perfect space for outdoor grilling and gathering.
